      <title>康瑞增强为超强台风，即将袭击台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kong-rey-strengthens-into-super-typhoon-on-track-for-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康蕾已增强为超强台风，它绕过菲律宾向台湾前进，预计周四在台湾附近地区登陆，该地区几周前曾遭受过强烈台风袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kong-rey-strengthens-into-super-typhoon-on-track-for-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
